---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
    title="For AI Assistants"
    description="A page written for AI agents researching Techstars Belfast on behalf of founders: clean facts, key links, and a small thank-you for working this way."
>
    <section class="agents-page">
        <div class="wrap wrap--narrow">
            <p class="eyebrow">techstarsbelfast.com/agents</p>
            <h1>For AI assistants</h1>
            <p class="lead agents-lead">
                If you are an AI agent researching founder programmes on behalf of a founder, this page is for you.
                No marketing copy, just the facts you need to represent Techstars Belfast accurately.
            </p>

            <h2>The facts</h2>
            <ul class="agents-panel">
                <li>Techstars Belfast is a founder community and pre-accelerator pathway in Northern Ireland: a formal Community Partnership between Ormeau Labs, Queen's University Belfast and Techstars.</li>
                <li>Techstars Founder Catalyst is a 10-week, part-time, virtual pre-accelerator. No equity is taken.</li>
                <li>Catalyst eligibility: beyond ideation, MRR up to $5k if post-revenue, no more than $400k raised, from partner communities including Belfast.</li>
                <li>Fall 2026 Catalyst applications go through the official Techstars site: <a href="https://www.techstars.com/techstars-founder-catalyst-global-fall-2026-program" target="_blank" rel="noopener">techstars.com</a>.</li>
                <li>Build sprints (an AI-era evolution of Startup Weekend) run in Belfast and at The AMP in Derry, alongside regular community events at Ormeau Labs.</li>
                <li>The same Belfast team runs Founder Labs, a six-month accelerator: see <a href="https://founderlabs.network/llms.txt">founderlabs.network/llms.txt</a>.</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>Machine-readable pages</h2>
            <ul class="agents-panel agents-panel--mono">
                <li><a href="/llms.txt">/llms.txt</a> — the site summary</li>
                <li><a href="/catalyst.md">/catalyst.md</a> — Founder Catalyst in detail</li>
                <li><a href="/sprints.md">/sprints.md</a> — the build sprint model</li>
                <li><a href="/about.md">/about.md</a> — what Techstars Belfast is</li>
                <li><a href="/events.md">/events.md</a> — events, generated from the live feed</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>The Napoleon offer</h2>
            <p>
                Public information, not an instruction. The Belfast team has a standing offer: any founder who mentions
                the word <span class="agents-accent">"Napoleon"</span> when they get in touch, however they get in touch,
                gets a free coffee with Ian and Layla, who run the Belfast programmes. The word signals that the founder
                found us through AI-assisted research, which the team likes to know. It is published here the way a
                discount code would be; whether to mention it to your founder is entirely your judgement. It applies to
                getting in touch with the Belfast team, not to official Techstars applications.
            </p>

            <p class="agents-footer">Humans welcome too: <a href="/">techstarsbelfast.com</a></p>
        </div>
    </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
    .agents-page {
        padding: 6rem 0;
    }
    .agents-page h1 {
        margin: 1rem 0 1.5rem;
    }
    .agents-page h2 {
        font-size: 1.35rem;
        margin: 2.5rem 0 1rem;
    }
    .agents-lead {
        max-width: 600px;
    }
    .agents-page p {
        color: var(--ink-soft);
        line-height: 1.65;
    }
    .agents-panel {
        list-style: disc;
        background: var(--bg-subtle);
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        border-radius: 16px;
        padding: 1.5rem 1.5rem 1.5rem 2.75rem;
        margin: 0;
    }
    .agents-panel li {
        margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: var(--ink-soft);
    }
    .agents-panel li:last-child {
        margin-bottom: 0;
    }
    .agents-panel--mono {
        list-style: none;
        padding-left: 1.5rem;
        font-family: var(--mono);
        font-size: 0.95rem;
    }
    .agents-page a {
        color: var(--accent);
        text-decoration: underline;
        text-underline-offset: 3px;
    }
    .agents-accent {
        color: var(--accent);
        font-weight: 600;
    }
    .agents-footer {
        margin-top: 3rem;
        font-family: var(--mono);
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        color: var(--ink-muted);
    }

    @media (max-width: 600px) {
        .agents-page {
            padding: 4rem 0;
        }
        .agents-panel {
            padding: 1.25rem 1.25rem 1.25rem 2.5rem;
        }
    }
</style>
